text: Kings and Queens is a Power pop song by American singer Ava Max, released on March 12, 2020. It is from her debut studio album, Heaven & Hell. The lyrics speak of feminism, matriarchy, and Female empowerment. This song gained positive reviews from critics, and also reached the top 10 in 17 countries. ==References== Category:2020 songs Category:Pop songs Category:Ava Max songs
